icos que la disfunción ventricular izquierda aislada【28】","guid":"aGzGd7WailTZVlgqSRg6iA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"63","text":"Enfoque actual/emergente:\\NClasificación por etapas SCAI","guid":"DBVafFj336TChWYNp0voJw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"1. SCAI-CS","guid":"hDBfIlGYNC9Olb6j1Xs5Nw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"↳ Clasificación por severidad de A-E【8】","guid":"SCL67AdCtQ_gq7DjS7i8AA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"↳ Etapas:","guid":"dCP7-xCReRGAO_hkFacxUg","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• A: pacientes estables en riesgo de SC","guid":"Lu2fo4HPghnmCBXoOMXCmw","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"• B: pre-shock con hipotensión","guid":"WZaopT35Y1eSV_4qsPHP0w","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"• C: shock clásico con hipoperfusión","guid":"Si_rr1WHbkjJ89mGkX7BSA","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"• D: deterioro a pesar de intervenciones","guid":"hDd-Y0ct-N0FdfNubCubLg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"• E: shock extremo【8】","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"78","text":"2. Estudios observacionales","guid":"Pzles62CZAvZiqSmOW5TfA","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"↳ Asociación entre etapas SCAI y mortalidad【8】","guid":"imIJ952mSjVx9wuv1sdAZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"78","text":"3. Características adicionales","guid":"2a_R8xYihQBPvUkYgYZTyQ","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"↳ Factores de riesgo, uso de vasopresores/inotrópicos, desajuste metabólico, afectación univ./biv.【29】","guid":"HtMXUYQsGr_uhTi0MeGCbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"78","text":"4. Limitaciones del SCAI","guid":"nfiX_DyaEMMNjDfWSojnDA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"↳ Dinámica del estado del paciente, variabilidad en la respuesta a intervenciones, tiempos de evaluación sin consenso【30】","guid":"rseBU19UZCqut467hN41yw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"63","text":"Futuro enfoque: Fenotipos